===Noun===
'''photosynthesis'''
# {{biology}} The [[process]] by which [[plant]]s and other [[organism]]s generate [[carbohydrate]]s and [[oxygen]] from [[carbon dioxide]] and [[water]] using [[light]] as a [[source]] of [[energy]].

